cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it using the metadata below."
title: "swatplus-hms-calibration: Hierarchical Multi-Scale Calibration of SWAT+ guided by Adaptive Sensitivity Analysis"
abstract: >-
  An R-based framework for hierarchical multi-scale calibration of SWAT+
  hydrological models. Couples Morris (LH-OAT) sensitivity screening
  re-executed at each temporal scale (annual water balance, monthly
  streamflow, daily streamflow) with sigma-informed parameter-range
  narrowing and cross-phase robustness filtering to manage equifinality.
  Built on top of SWATrunR.
type: software
authors:
